title: Free Scotch Felt Pads, Boogie Wipes from Target Sample Spot
text:
Free Scotch Felt Pads, Boogie Wipes from Target Sample Spot Free sample of Scotch Felt Pads. Doreen Christensen Sun Sentinel Get two free deluxe samples from Target. 
Get two free deluxe samples from Target. 
First, sign up for Scotch Felt Pads, which go on the bottom of chairs or furniture to protect floors. 
Second, sign up to get a sample of Boogie Wipes for baby, saline nose wipes for kids. 
Answer a few questions and the products should arrive in 3-5 weeks.

Two Trader Joe's stores are soon opening in South Florida. The chain, which stocks more than 3,000 private-label brands, dropped anchor in Davie on Friday, Oct. 9, at 2296 S. University Drive. The second location opens at 1560 N. Federal Highway in Fort Lauderdale on Oct. 15. (Doreen Christensen)
